# Repositories

## Pattern

- Interface in `repositories/interfaces/I*.java`
- Implementation in `repositories/implementations/*Repository.java`
- `@Repository` + `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`

## Procedure calls

- Name: exact match `usp_*` from Database repo
- Register every parameter before `execute()`
- Reads: parse `Object[]` rows into DTOs (column order = SELECT order in proc)
- Multi-result: `do { ... } while (query.hasMoreResults());`

## Writes

- `@Transactional` on create/update/delete methods
- Return generated IDs from first result set when proc returns `LAST_INSERT_ID()` or `id` column

## Do not

- Use `createNativeQuery` for business CRUD
- Swallow SQL exceptions — let `GlobalExceptionHandler` wrap or map
- Instantiate repositories in services manually (constructor injection only)
